A Bank Spain spokesman qualified bank statement announcing extension reserve requirement convertible peseta fund held bank , saying move applied future rise current balance .
`` The 19 pct reserve requirement applied increase bank 's convertible peseta fund , '' spokesman said .
Convertible peseta fund previously exempt reserve requirement .
The spokesman said measure intended curb influx short-term foreign speculative capital threatened government 's money supply growth target .
